      "text": "So all in all, it was a not unhappy time for you there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a not unhappy time because I made good friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
